title: How do I clear my browser's cache and browsing history?
answer:
Open the browser, touch ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110616) > Settings > Privacy & security > Clear cache or Clear history.
